HEADWORD: Ornithoscelida
<hw>Or*ni`tho*scel"i*da</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>'o`rnis</grk>, <grk>'o`rniqos</grk>, a bird +
